<p>I am using scale and crop for creating a new video. The problem is the <code>nullsrc</code>'s size is greater than the input, leaving a blinking green background. How can I change the blinking green background to black?</p>  <p>here is my code:</p>  <p><code>ffmpeg -y -i 1.mov -filter_complex "nullsrc=size=640x480 [base]; [0:v] setpts=PTS-STARTPTS, scale=320x480 [left]; [base][left] overlay=shortest=0:x=160" -c:v libx264 -t 5 output.mp4</code></p>